  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice — factual stub. Design only; no raw genetic readouts\n     are shown. Draft until ready. -->\n<p class=\"\">A single-page, Tufte-styled report that turns my own 30× whole-genome sequencing into something legible — an academic-paper layout with D3 visualizations instead of a wall of raw variant tables. The screenshot is the report's masthead and overview; the actual readouts stay private.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Comprehensive Genomic Analysis — the report masthead and overview, Tufte/D3 styling\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/ejfox-genome/report.png\" alt=\"Comprehensive Genomic Analysis — the report masthead and overview, Tufte/D3 styling\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/ejfox-genome/report.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/ejfox-genome/report.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/ejfox-genome/report.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/ejfox-genome/report.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Comprehensive Genomic Analysis — the report masthead and overview, Tufte/D3 styling\" width=\"1440\" height=\"1000\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.96deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1440×1000\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Comprehensive Genomic Analysis — the report masthead and overview, Tufte/D3 styling</figcaption>\n</figure>",
